============
bluetti_mqtt
============

This tool will (eventually) provide an MQTT interface to Bluetti power
stations. This would enable status and control through Home Assistant or
another system.

Installation
------------

.. code-block:: bash

    $ pip install bluetti_mqtt
    $ bluetti-logger -h
